<!--
  --- Question 5 ---
  This component represents the fifth question in the quiz.
-->

<div class="question-card" id="card-4" data-qid="4" data-type="single">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="q-number">Q 05</span>
    <span class="q-tag single">Single Choice</span>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      A new network administrator has been asked to enter a banner message on a Cisco device. What is the fastest way a network administrator could test whether the banner is properly configured?
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-4">
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Enter CTRL-Z at the privileged mode prompt.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Power cycle the device.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Exit privileged EXEC mode and press Enter.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="3">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">D</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Exit global configuration mode.</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="4">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">E</span>
        <span class="opt-text">Reboot the device.</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="submit-wrap" style="display: none;">
      <button class="submit-btn" id="submit-4" disabled>Submit Answer</button>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation" id="exp-4">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-4"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        The fastest way to test whether the banner is properly configured is to:
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Exit privileged EXEC mode and press Enter</strong> &mdash; This will display the banner message immediately.</li>
        </ul>
        Power cycling or rebooting the device would also display the banner, but these methods are slower and unnecessary for a quick test.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pagination-controls">
      <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-4">Previous</button>
      <span class="page-indicator">5 / 5</span>
      <button class="nav-btn" id="next-4">Next</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
